npc1: Welcome! Before you head out, let me show you the basics.
npc1: Press [A] and [D] to move left and right.
npc1: Press [Space] to jump. Press [Space] again while in the air for a double jump!
npc1: When you find other survivors out there, press [F] to talk to them. They know things you need to hear.
npc1: Keep an eye on your health bar — don't let the creatures out there wear you down.
npc1: The portal ahead leads to Stage 1. The city is in trouble.
npc1: Something corrupted it. Something from deep inside the internet.
npc1: You are the only one who can trace it back to the source.
npc1: Good luck out there.
